    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "9b46c350_6120a711",
        "filename": "autoroll/go/autoroll-fe/main.go",
        "patchSetId": 5
      },
      "lineNbr": 209,
      "author": {
        "id": 5015
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-04-25T15:01:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Just picked it arbitrarily, based on:\n- Normally we have fewer than 20 or so not-yet-rolled revisions\n- We probably won\u0027t (shouldn\u0027t, anyway) request manual rolls for every not-yet-rolled revision\n\nPossible alternatives:\n\n1. Make the limit equal to len(status.NotRolledRevisions), based on the fact that we don\u0027t care about manual rolls to past revisions (those aren\u0027t displayed on the UI; whether we want to support that in the future is a potential question), and that we probably won\u0027t have multiple manual rolls to the same revision.\n2. Just load the unfinished requests here, rather than a number of recent rolls.\n3. Only load requests which are associated with one of the NotRolledRevisions.",
      "parentUuid": "a9afeed5_21ad685b",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 209,
        "startChar": 70,
        "endLine": 209,
        "endChar": 95
      },
      "revId": "8cb6080c145a56ba3c6f8c6b23b49df37e947ba1",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "9cac89fd_0829d84f",
        "filename": "autoroll/go/autoroll-fe/main.go",
        "patchSetId": 5
      },
      "lineNbr": 209,
      "author": {
        "id": 5145
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-04-25T15:12:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "(3) looks like the best option but not sure how difficult it will be.\nMaking it simple and doing len(status.NotRolledRevisions) also works for me.\nUpto you.",
      "parentUuid": "9b46c350_6120a711",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 209,
        "startChar": 70,
        "endLine": 209,
        "endChar": 95
      },
      "revId": "8cb6080c145a56ba3c6f8c6b23b49df37e947ba1",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
